      • long2ShortEntrySet

        public ObjectSortedSet<Long2ShortMap.Entry> long2ShortEntrySet()
        Description copied from interface: Long2ShortMap
        Returns a type-specific set view of the mappings contained in this map.

        This method is necessary because there is no inheritance along type parameters: it is thus impossible to strengthen Long2ShortMap.entrySet() so that it returns an ObjectSet of type-specific entries (the latter makes it possible to access keys and values with type-specific methods).

        Specified by:
        long2ShortEntrySet in interface Long2ShortMap
        Specified by:
